## 8. Main User Journeys

### 8.1 Employee Creates Work into Memory

```text
Login
→ Home / Department Workspace
→ Upload file or create note
→ System stores source
→ System previews content
→ System extracts text/data
→ System generates summary/tags/metadata
→ Employee reviews basic info
→ Submit for review
→ Department Lead approves/rejects
→ Approved content becomes Work Memory
→ AI can answer from it with source
```

### 8.2 Department Lead Reviews Memory

```text
Login
→ See Pending Reviews
→ Open submitted item
→ Compare source with extracted summary
→ Check title/tags/visibility/sensitivity
→ Approve / Reject / Request changes
→ If approved: embed into Work Memory
→ Activity + audit created
```

### 8.3 New Employee Handover

```text
Department Lead generates Handover Report
→ New employee reads report
→ New employee asks AI follow-up
→ AI answers only from allowed department sources
```

### 8.4 Finance OCR to Record

```text
Upload receipt
→ OCR extracts fields
→ User reviews
→ Finance lead confirms
→ Create finance record
→ Dashboard updates
→ Approved finance info enters Work Memory
→ AI answers with source
```

### 8.5 Field Mobile Capture to Server

```text
Assign field task
→ Staff records data/photo on mobile
→ Save local/offline
→ Return to office / connect LAN
→ Sync to server
→ Department Lead reviews
→ Approved record becomes Work Memory
```

### 8.6 AI Chat

```text
Open AI Chat
→ Select active department/scope
→ Ask question
→ Resolve permission
→ Retrieve allowed sources
→ AI answers with citation
→ User opens source
→ User may save answer as note/activity
```

